# Local artifacts (scratch outputs at repo root).
# NOTE: the patterns below are anchored to repo root so the same file names
# inside iterations/v*/ remain tracked. Tracked iteration artifacts are the
# citable fixtures behind each version of the paper; the root copies are
# whatever the latest local run happened to produce.
